comment: /**  * Returns the names of the hosts storing the data this input split refers to  *  * @return the names of the hosts storing the data this input split refers to  */
code: /**  * Returns the names of the hosts storing the data this input split refers to  *  * @return the names of the hosts storing the data this input split refers to  */ public String[] getHostnames() {     return this.hostnames. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj == this) {         return true.     } else if (obj instanceof LocatableInputSplit) {         LocatableInputSplit other = (LocatableInputSplit) obj.         return other.splitNumber == this.splitNumber && Arrays.deepEquals(other.hostnames, this.hostnames).     } else {         return false.     } }
@Override public String toString() {     return "Locatable Split (" + splitNumber + ") at " + Arrays.toString(this.hostnames). }
